item.title: My Shiny Dashboard, Milwaukee Beer
item.description: Milwaukee Beer - Inspired by my Job Hunt I’m excited to launch my latest Shiny app - “Milwaukee Beer” - which I made to learn shinydashboard. Due to my decision to return to the USA and hunt for a career in data, I decided to add another project to my portfolio.
